<br>
The greatest ac/hp plate set is found in Tak and is sold for 1492 adventure points per item. Each pieces also have slots 2, 2 and 3 for augments. With the good augments its possible to have a full set of armor on par with Elemental equipment.<br>
<br>
For reference :<br>
The best Tak BP is sold for 1492 and has this for stats :<br>
Royal Attendant Breastplate of the Sand<br>
AC:69, Sta:13, Cha:11, Wis:10, Int:10, HP:100, Mana:100, CR:12, MR:12, PR:12, type2,type2,type3 <br>
<br>
The Mir BP is sold for 760 and has this for stats :<br>
Malevolent Breastplate of Suffering<br>
AC:63, Str:10, Dex:9, Wis:8, Int:8, HP:75, Mana:75, FR:9, DR:9, PR:9, type1,type2,type3 <br>
<br>
The MM BP is sold for 150 and has this for stats :<br>
Death Embracer's Breastplate<br>
AC:40, Str:6, Sta:6, Wis:6, Int:6, HP:25, Mana:25, FR:5, DR:5, type1,type1,type3 <br>
<br>
The Ruj BP is sold for 48 and has this for stats :<br>
Agressor's Breastplate<br>
AC:32, Sta:5, Wis:5, HP:10, Mana:10, type1,type3 <br>
<br>
Another Tak BP is sold for 20 and has this for stats :<br>
Sand-Coated Breastplate<br>
AC:25, Str:4, Wis:3, Int:3, MR:4, type1,type3 <br>
